duration-200 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/knowledge\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">🗃️</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">Knowledge</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">企业知识智能检索</div></div></a></div></nav><div class=\"shrink-0 p-4 border-t border-gray-100 bg-white\"><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400\"><div>版本 v1.0.0</div><div class=\"mt-1\">© 2026 AI Tools Center</div></div></div></aside><main class=\"flex-1 ml-72\"><div class=\"p-8\"><header class=\"mb-8\"><h1 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2\">探索智能工具，提升工作效率</h1><p class=\"text-gray-500\">发现并使用优质的 AI 能力资源</p></header><section class=\"mb-10\"><h2 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4\">🎯 能力概览</h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4\"><a class=\"bg-white rounded-xl p-5 border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-md hover:border-blue-200 transition-all group\" href=\"/skill\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\"><div class=\"text-3xl\">✨</div><div class=\"flex-1\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-900 group-hover:text-blue-600\">Skill</h3><svg class=\"w-4 h-4 text-gray-400 group-hover:text-blue-500 transition-colors\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 5l7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></div><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1\">可复用的能力模块</p><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 mt-2 line-clamp-2\">Skill 是封装好的 AI 能力单元，可直接调用完成特定任务，如文本处理、数据分析、代码生成等。</p></div></div></a><a class=\"bg-white rounded-xl p-5 border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-md hover:border-blue-200 transition-all group\" href=\"/mcp\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\"><div class=\"text-3xl\">🔌</div><div class=\"flex-1\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-900 group-hover:text-blue-600\">MCP</h3><svg class=\"w-4 h-4 text-gray-400 group-hover:text-blue-500 transition-colors\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 5l7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></div><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1\">外部服务快速接入</p><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 mt-2 line-clamp-2\">MCP (Model Context Protocol) 让 AI 能够连接外部工具和服务，如数据库、API、文件系统等。</p></div></div></a><a class=\"bg-white rounded-xl p-5 border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-md hover:border-blue-200 transition-all group\" href=\"/agent\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\"><div class=\"text-3xl\">🤖</div><div class=\"flex-1\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-900 group-hover:text-blue-600\">Agent</h3><svg class=\"w-4 h-4 text-gray-400 group-hover:text-blue-500 transition-colors\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 5l7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></div><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1\">自主决策的 AI 助手</p><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 mt-2 line-clamp-2\">Agent 具有自主决策能力，能理解目标并规划执行步骤，自动完成复杂任务链。</p></div></div></a><a class=\"bg-white rounded-xl p-5 border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-md hover:border-blue-200 transition-all group\" href=\"/prompt\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\"><div class=\"text-3xl\">📝</div><div class=\"flex-1\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-900 group-hover:text-blue-600\">Prompt</h3><svg class=\"w-4 h-4 text-gray-400 group-hover:text-blue-500 transition-colors\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 5l7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></div><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1\">高效沟通的模板</p><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 mt-2 line-clamp-2\">Prompt 是经过优化的提示词模板，帮助用户更准确地与 AI 沟通，获得高质量输出。</p></div></div></a><a class=\"bg-white rounded-xl p-5 border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-md hover:border-blue-200 transition-all group\" href=\"/workflow\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\"><div class=\"text-3xl\">🔄</div><div class=\"flex-1\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-900 group-hover:text-blue-600\">Workflow</h3><svg class=\"w-4 h-4 text-gray-400 group-hover:text-blue-500 transition-colors\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 5l7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></div><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1\">多步骤任务编排</p><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 mt-2 line-clamp-2\">Workflow 支持将多个能力串联成工作流，自动化执行复杂的多步骤任务。</p></div></div></a><a class=\"bg-white rounded-xl p-5 border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-md hover:border-blue-200 transition-all group\" href=\"/knowledge\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\"><div class=\"text-3xl\">📚</div><div class=\"flex-1\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-900 group-hover:text-blue-600\">Knowledge</h3><svg class=\"w-4 h-4 text-gray-400 group-hover:text-blue-500 transition-colors\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 5l7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></div><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1\">企业知识智能检索</p><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 mt-2 line-clamp-2\">Knowledge 构建企业专属知识库，让 AI 基于私有数据进行智能问答和内容生成。</p></div></div></a></div></section><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 mb-12\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\"><span class=\"text-gray-500 text-sm\">Skill 总数</span><span class=\"text-xl\">✨</span></div><div class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-blue-600\">5</div><div class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 mt-1\">可直接使用</div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow\"><div class=\"flex items